Search.Name: 13-2 object in diagram how have className

RootTable.Filter: SELECT o.Name AS ObjectName, c.Name AS ClassName,o.Package_ID AS ObjectPackageID , p.Package_ID AS DiagramPackageID, d.Name AS DiagramName FROM ((((t_diagram AS d INNER JOIN t_diagramobjects AS do ON d.Diagram_ID = do.Diagram_ID) INNER JOIN t_object AS o ON do.Object_ID = o.Object_ID) INNER JOIN t_object AS c ON o.Classifier = c.Object_ID) INNER JOIN t_package AS p ON d.Package_ID = p.Package_ID) WHERE o.Package_ID <> p.Package_ID;

SELECT DISTINCT o.Object_ID, o.Name AS Object_Name, a.Name AS Attribute_Name, m.Name AS Method_Name FROM(((( t_object o LEFT JOIN t_attribute a ON o.Object_ID = a.Object_ID) LEFT JOIN t_operation m ON o.Object_ID = m.Object_ID) LEFT JOIN t_diagramobjects do ON o.Object_ID = do.Object_ID) LEFT JOIN t_diagram d ON do.Diagram_ID = d.Diagram_ID) ORDER BY o.Object_ID;
